summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of One Hundred Sixty-two & 50/100 $162.50 Dollars, or so much there of as may be necessary, from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, to complete the improvement of West Seventy-third Street, et al, by grading and curbing as provided for by Ordinance No. 18178, creating Local Improvement District No. 1712.
